{
  "Id": 880000010,
  "Name": "燃燒的光玉",
  "Description": "馬琪正在嘗試聯絡你，而這似乎與先行公約最近籌劃的名為《第二索拉》的大型專案有關……",
  "MaleTexture": "",
  "FemaleTexture": "",
  "AreaIcon": "",
  "QuestId": 880000010,
  "ShowQuestList": [],
  "QuestDesc": "馬琪正在嘗試聯絡你，而這似乎與先行公約最近籌劃的名為《第二索拉》的大型專案有關……",
  "Conditions": [],
  "Chapters": [
    {
      "Dialogues": [
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "今天要製作的遊戲場景是這樣的……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "在這一卷的末尾，主角終於要和無冠者展開決戰。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 3,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "原著裡寫道「……黑暗如山般壓向了我們……我們的劍與矛早已斷裂，法杖上的寶石也已破碎……」",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 4,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "「而無冠者的身影幾乎遮蔽了夜空……它睥睨著我們，目光如刀……」",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 5,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "「……縱使只有手中<color=highlight>燃燒的光玉</span>，我們亦要邁向那巨壁一般的敵人……」",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 6,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "「……若荒野無處可歸，那便行軍踏向這世界的盡頭。若長夜無光，那便舉刀揮向那無能的月輪。」",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 261,
              "PlotLineKey": "聽得我熱血沸騰。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 262,
              "PlotLineKey": "很期待這個場景製作出來。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 263,
              "PlotLineKey": "這裡該播一段氣勢磅礴的音樂。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 7,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "作為第一卷的高潮，第一次看到這裡時我和你一樣激動。 我也很期待在遊戲中還原這個場景。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 8,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "但是只有一點，大家都想像不出<color=highlight>燃燒的光玉</span>的樣子……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 9,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "雖然在之前的章節也有提到過它，但作者並沒有詳細地描寫它的外觀。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 10,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "要是能找到它的參考的話，大家應該就能還原出決戰的場景了。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 11,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "如果你有找到合適的東西的話，可以隨時過來交給我。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Dialogues": [
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "原來如此……這個東西的確很符合我對燃燒的光玉的想像。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "我現在就把這個交給開發人員。 相信有了它，大家就能夠製作出最後的場景了。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "Speaker_undefined",
          "PlotLineKey": "",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "到這裡，小說裡天城篇的場景就全部製作完成了。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "非常感謝你給予先行公約的幫助，{PlayerName}。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 392,
              "PlotLineKey": "場景非常好看。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 3
            },
            {
              "TextId": 393,
              "PlotLineKey": "期待能儘早玩到遊戲。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 4
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 3,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "我也覺得很好看。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 5
        },
        {
          "Id": 4,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "我也很期待。 等有了進一步的消息，我會馬上告訴你的。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 5
        },
        {
          "Id": 5,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "順帶一提，卡爾先生也知道了你的名字，說如果有機會一定要見你一面。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 394,
              "PlotLineKey": "能和作者見面是我的榮幸。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 6
            },
            {
              "TextId": 395,
              "PlotLineKey": "他是不是要給我什麼特別禮物？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 7
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 6,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "卡爾先生也表示很感謝你幫助他的小說改編遊戲的開發。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 8
        },
        {
          "Id": 7,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "這我就不清楚了，等你以後見到卡爾先生了親自問他吧。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 8
        },
        {
          "Id": 8,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "總之，目前事情就告一段落了。 但是……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 396,
              "PlotLineKey": "但是什麼？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 9,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "開發組的成員都很喜歡你提供的物品參考。 在遊戲之後的章節如果還有需要，還可以再拜託你嗎？",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 397,
              "PlotLineKey": "當然可以。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 398,
              "PlotLineKey": "價錢到位，都好說。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 10,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "那就太好了，你可以放心，先約一定不會在報酬上吝嗇的。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 11,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "那麼，下次見啦，{PlayerName}，期待和你之後的合作。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Dialogues": [
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "其實……關於今天的參考物品，有位書迷有一些自己的看法。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 345,
              "PlotLineKey": "是哪位？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 346,
              "PlotLineKey": "在哪個位置？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "他的名字叫斜陽，白天應該在今州書院附近就可以找到他。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 3,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "他對小說的諸多場景都很有自己的看法，也給我們提了很多意見，可是……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 347,
              "PlotLineKey": "可是什麼？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 4
            },
            {
              "TextId": 348,
              "PlotLineKey": "他很難相處嗎。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 5
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 4,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "可是……他說的話很難懂。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 6
        },
        {
          "Id": 5,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "不，那倒不是。 他只是說的話很難懂……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 6
        },
        {
          "Id": 6,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "大家雖然能夠感受到他對《第二索拉》的熱情，但都覺得和他溝通起來很困難。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 7,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "但是我感覺，如果是你的話，也許可以聽懂他在說什麼。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 349,
              "PlotLineKey": "我去找找他看看。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 9
            },
            {
              "TextId": 350,
              "PlotLineKey": "我的確很懂中二病和謎語人。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": 8
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 8,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "雖然我不懂你說的詞是什麼意思，但聽起來你很有信心的樣子。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [],
          "JumpToId": 9
        },
        {
          "Id": 9,
          "Speaker": "馬琪",
          "PlotLineKey": "那麼就拜託你啦。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "Dialogues": [
        {
          "Id": 1,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "那無能的月輪，是主角對無冠者不仁的控訴……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 2,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "而燃燒的光玉，是寂夜裡綻放的光明的新芽……",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 294,
              "PlotLineKey": "好！ 大文豪！",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 295,
              "PlotLineKey": "好難懂……",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 3,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "終於有人主動來問我《第二索拉》的事了……天地可鑒，我一定是這本書最忠誠的粉絲。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 4,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "只有這本書中的廣闊世界，能承載我如不歇之泉般時刻滿溢的文采！",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 296,
              "PlotLineKey": "那你覺得燃燒的光玉是什麼？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 5,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "從聽說你幫助先約開始製作遊戲起，我就料到，你一定會來問我這個問題。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 297,
              "PlotLineKey": "為什麼你這麼肯定？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 6,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "為什麼？ 因為這燃燒的光玉，是那場震天撼地的決戰裡逆轉局勢的關鍵！",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 7,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "如此不可一世的寶貝，你在俗世裡自然是尋不到參考物的。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 298,
              "PlotLineKey": "那要在哪裡才能找到？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 299,
              "PlotLineKey": "還請大師給我一個明示。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 8,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "既然你如此誠心地發問了，我就告訴你……這種東西，只有在那變幻莫測的<ano=聲之領域>索諾拉</ano>中才能找到。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 300,
              "PlotLineKey": "聲之領域……",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 301,
              "PlotLineKey": "大師高明！",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 9,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "但這可為難不了作為忠實粉絲的我，我早已備好了東西。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 10,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "現在，我就可以把這個珍貴無比的參考物送給你。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 11,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "但是，我有個條件。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 302,
              "PlotLineKey": "什麼條件？",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 303,
              "PlotLineKey": "大師請講。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 12,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "那就是……你問問馬琪，能否把我斜陽的大名也附屬在遊戲的感謝名單上。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        },
        {
          "Id": 13,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "我頭號粉絲的名頭，必須要人盡皆知才行。",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 304,
              "PlotLineKey": "我可以幫你問問。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            },
            {
              "TextId": 305,
              "PlotLineKey": "這個事情先行公約說了才算數。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 14,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "反正……辛苦你幫我問問。 我斜陽，盡人事，聽天命！",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": [
            {
              "TextId": 306,
              "PlotLineKey": "好的大師。",
              "PlayVoice": false,
              "JumpToId": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "Id": 15,
          "Speaker": "斜陽",
          "PlotLineKey": "東西在這，你拿去吧。 答應我的事可別忘了！",
          "PlayVoice": false,
          "Options": []
        }
      ]
    },
